                <note rend="inline" type="source">825.51/1284a: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        Ambassador in Chile</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Bowers</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1940-12-04T13:00:00-05:00"
                            >December 4, 1940—1 p.m.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>216. With Reference to press reports that the Chilean Government has officially
                    suspended amortization of the foreign debt to divert funds to the Exchange
                    Control Commission, please expedite full report.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Hull</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
